1. Purpose

This repository is shared as a personal learning workspace for Java full-stack
development, including frontend fundamentals, Java, Spring Boot, databases,
APIs, authentication, testing, deployment, system design, AI engineering, and
portfolio project practice.

The intention is to help learners study, practice, build, revise, and prepare
for real software development work while respecting the effort that went into
organizing and writing this material.

